{"tid":872203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"薄得像紙！日本神級麵包師1條吐司切88片","createTime":"2018-10-22T13:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T14:17:59.000Z","uid":32511,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dc26f12642fc3a40574a0c2e3b55f83b3b10871a","tid":872203,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T13:57:52.000Z","msg":"麵包店的吐司常常會分厚、薄兩種，日本1位麵包師傅竟運用高超的刀工，將1條吐司切成88片，片片薄到透光。<br />\n <br />\n綜合媒體報導，日本千葉縣1間麵包店「小倉烘焙坊」的麵包師傅Jun，在麵包店工作的資歷長達8年，因為時常有客人要求要切出指定厚度的吐司，讓Jun練出了一手好刀工，並突發奇想創立了「薄切吐司大賽」，想挑戰自己的技術。<br />\n <br />\n在第1屆「薄切吐司大賽」中，Jun成功將1斤（日本單位，約454公克）的吐司切成47片，每片只有大約2毫米（mm）厚；第2屆「薄切吐司大賽」時，Jun進步到切出了77片，每片僅有1.5毫米（mm）厚；而最近1次的第3屆賽事，Jun竟然破紀錄地切出了88片，每片都薄到透光。<br />\n <br />\n他切出超薄片吐司之後，順勢將薄片吐司加工成千層蛋糕、千層三明治、炸吐司餅乾等商品，在麵包店內販售，不同的品項每位客人限購1-2個不等。也有不少網友希望Jun能挑戰切出100片吐司，但Jun表示這有點太難，未來可能會先挑戰切90片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/215742_081a3d2e2003ac6890ce76b346bdcfdf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F215742_081a3d2e2003ac6890ce76b346bdcfdf.png&h=6f4cded8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/215745_0742b3bfe08435ef47b9bf453bd31e92.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F215745_0742b3bfe08435ef47b9bf453bd31e92.png&h=8d5a2377&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/215748_f3bdc3eb763ed532fefa141063fa5299.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F215748_f3bdc3eb763ed532fefa141063fa5299.png&h=28156af2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30bcc184fb18985571703f1bcef45d7697d137d6","tid":872203,"uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T13:58:46.000Z","msg":"樓下麵包鋪冇哂雞尾包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d8b5b84c124c0c5d0164a46b331aaccd813d22","tid":872203,"uid":30966,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"如果調返轉係香港麵包師傅 又要比Child登仔批評了"},{"pid":"7be972b56677e4ed57499414552045112eae8e69","tid":872203,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:00:30.000Z","msg":"香港師傅：塊包切唔到底你咪用手撕開囉！又唔係豬肉！"},{"pid":"6578215607ec684af9cbddb26fd010f5df3bbdb7","tid":872203,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"好撚小家嘅技術"},{"pid":"df658c2d46067006f3f663140763645a51f4c17b","tid":872203,"uid":85557,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:02:36.000Z","msg":"要放幾多日先切到咁薄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe852d5dfbfdfdaebd557d85fc0f4b23be9e001","tid":872203,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:03:41.000Z","msg":"切包皮技術一流"},{"pid":"bc7dc014ee8426edb5f19f282ac3795ca25c6c8c","tid":872203,"uid":73722,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"黎香港人工實好高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班鐸縮商家佬實請佢黎整多士慳成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdb463dff3428da0b314778692377d6142ad97a","tid":872203,"uid":51134,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/220913_3981ac499703dcac12fb347ca803728d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F220913_3981ac499703dcac12fb347ca803728d.gif&h=f74f78c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab86b9af286ca41d5b73015f3e16eb4421ccbb9e","tid":872203,"uid":164240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecdb463dff3428da0b314778692377d6142ad97a","tid":872203,"uid":51134,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/220913_3981ac4997